{"tid":1612003,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"黎棟國：警員電光火石間或未有特別作瞄準","createTime":"2019-10-02T06:15:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T06:44:54.000Z","uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"73cf4870ba2cc16bc1cf400f1fafb1f7f0735821","tid":1612003,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T06:15:19.000Z","msg":"黎棟國：警員電光火石間或未有特別作瞄準<br />\n<br />\n#港聞 在北京，保安局前局長黎棟國指，警員星期日向示威者開槍是合情、合理、符合指引。他指警員當時生命受威脅，在電光火石間或未有特別作出瞄準。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=364816\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D364816&d=zBKsoIV%2FeLhWSsP5H2J%2Bmt8yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=b17a5cd3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D364816&h=2e175be0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=364816</a>"},{"pid":"1cf1ebb78ffbb7205099c2d5d309b991c838811c","tid":1612003,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T06:15:46.000Z","msg":"收皮啦"},{"pid":"d5bcdb41d4671861ad9cdb22df4b3b19009244f7","tid":1612003,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T06:15:57.000Z","msg":"又助攻<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f65c611a8774e37d98bf42b92594ca8a2c1590f2","tid":1612003,"uid":103960,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T06:16:28.000Z","msg":"開撚左兩槍 仲要追撚住呀<br />\n電光火石？<br />\n食屎啦"},{"pid":"3a493c4719c333940c871953c0f361a18628d107","tid":1612003,"uid":58140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T06:16:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">電光火石</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">電光火石</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">電光火石</span